        "localization": {
          "name": "Stealth Zone",
          "description": "Each ally with a Stealth Strike type active skill is healed for HP equal to 500% of the user's Attack, becomes Enraged, and gains Stealth with a Stealth Shield. Allies gain 3 Spirit for each other affected ally. Cannot be used if the user already has both Stealth and a Stealth Shield.\n\n-Stealth Strike type active skills are any skills that are unlocked while their user has Stealth.\n-Stealth Shields prevent the next non-stealth status effect a unit would gain while Stealthed from applying.\n-Stealth will overwrite other status effects on affected units. Stealthed units ignore the next enemy attack that would damage more than 1 target. Any damage will remove stealth.\n-Enraged units have their Attack increased to 1.5x until the end of their next turn. This will overwrite the effects of other Enrage skills on affected units.",
